531.text:
開拓局から公式のダンジョンの調査依頼です。
『陽炎の谷』にある『ボルオム遺跡』の調査をお願いします。
砂漠の中にありながら気温が安定しており、野生動物が集まる遺跡としても知られています。が、ここを狩り場と見た凶悪なモンスターたちも集まっているようです。
周囲地域の安全確保のためにも、『猛掘！　ボルオム遺跡』を実施してください。
上級調査は難易度の高い依頼です。挑戦する際にはくれぐれも気をつけてくださいね。
ご協力をお願いいたします！

◆クリア対象
『猛掘！　ボルオム遺跡』

532.text:
開拓局から公式のダンジョンの調査依頼です。
『鎮まりの山麓』にある『機跡の谷』の調査をお願いします。
内部の防衛機構が突如起動し、バファリアの遺産が次々に現れて外部まで影響しかねない状況です。
原因の特定のため、『凶闘！　機跡の谷』を実施して、ひとまず現場の混乱を収拾してください。
上級調査は難易度の高い依頼です。挑戦する際にはくれぐれも気をつけてくださいね。
ご協力をお願いいたします！

◆クリア対象

24.text:
In Giant Dragon's Claw Marks, he encountered a legendary monster, Avalitia. In addition, a mysterious boy Merlofof, who flew from the sky, heard the word "visitors". 
 Are these related to the lost memory?

25.text:
I was able to hear about the "visitors" from Bufferrier priest Walkin and his apprentice Milrene. 
 "Visitors" are Gentiles with special power. 
 It seems that the secret is in the Bahamar Highlands, Sacred Pillar of the Gods, the largest sacred place in Bufferrier.

26.text:
In "Sacred Pillar of the Gods", I met Aerines and Tyris, who came from the future 1000 years later. 
 They will release Avalitia and save this star from the future of destruction.

 "SANCTUARY OF DIVINE BLESSING" is still unknown, and the cult has decided that further investigations are needed. 
 The Defense Organization must avoid danger to oracle shrine maiden and priests. 
 Follow the route to the innermost part and give a detailed investigation. 

 ◆ Clear target 
 "Leaf eyebrows! Sanctuary of Divine Blessing]

446.text:
I am Ariane. I'm making perfumes with Asterliese. 
 Recently, I have been refused a part of the order. 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E027_01_0_03001"/> is in "Sun-Dapted Forest Path", and it seems that the plant that is the material is freezing ... 
 I can't maintain the quality I can sell. 
 I wonder if <value type = "enemyname" id = "E027_01_03001"/> will be defeated so that the materials are included. 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E027_01_0_03001"/> 3 ("Sun-Dapped Forest Path")

447.text:
My name is Danae, a pharmacist of MinsterHorn. 
 The other day, I was asked for a cough medicine by a Salamzart adventurer, but it seems that it is not just a cold. 
 Perhaps the dust was sucked in for a long time and the throat was damaged. Normal cough drugs cannot be expected to be effective. 
 In "Forest of Will-O'-The-Wisps", collect 5 "Brisian flowers" required for medicine. 
 Hopefully, it will be a great help of the desert people. Thank you. 

 ◆ Collection target (where you can get) 
 5 brisian flowers ("FOREST OF WILL-O'-THE-WISPS") / Plants

448.text:
It is a paint craftsman Detrev. 
 I'm making paint from ore with Ritze, but recently many adventurers who have requested procurement have failed. 
 Everyone says, "<Value type =" enemyname "id =" E005_00_00_03001 "/>. 
 Even though there were veterans, what happened to losing <value type = "enemyname" id = "E005_00_03001"/>? 
 What I want is the Robinite Mining that can be obtained in UNENDING RAIN FOREST. 
 However, it is troublesome not to be able to get it in the future. 
 By the way, can you defeat the strange <Value Type = "EnemyName" id = "E005_00_00_03001"/>? 
 It's a troublesome request, but I'll ask you. 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E005_00_00_03001"/> 1 ("UNENDING RAIN FOREST") 
 ◆ Collection target (where you can get) 
 5 Robinite ore ("UNENDING RAIN FOREST") / Mineral

449.text:
Mostly. Meidosue who helps the team formation. 
 Do you know "<value type =" enemyname "id =" E023_00_04_03001 "/>? 
 It looks like a monster. A number of skilled teams will fail to defeat. 
 The number of teams who say that they will be dissolved without confidence is increasing. Honma, Ikuyawa. 
 Can you go to "The Value Type =" E023_00_04_04_03001 "/>" to go to "Fusen's Stage"? 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E023_00_04_04_03001"/> 1

450.text:
Durger, an adventurer. Ask for cooperation because it was bad. 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" id = "E001_05_03001"/> is living in "Scarlet Dyeing Forest" of Montegnor Valley. 
 They seem to be trying to expand their territory as the number has increased recently. 
 If you are not good, you will be damaged on the highway and RITZE. 
 5 bodies are fine. <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E001_05_00_03001"/> Can you reduce the number? 
 I'll defeat it with all my might! 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E001_05_00_03001"/> 5 ("Scarlet Forest")

451.text:
Well, it's Aegis Fighter COZE. 
 Giant Dragon's Claw Marks was informed that the adventurer team had trouble and became unable to move. 
 I want to help immediately, but they seem to have been in a deep and distress. As you know, there is a ridiculous monster in the back there. 
 Can you ask for "<Value Type =" EnemyName "ID =" E002_03_00_03001 "/>? 
 If he gets his attention, he will go to rescue in the meantime. 
 I do not abandon those who seek help. 
 You don't have to worry if you help me. Please, ask! 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E002_03_00_03001"/> 1 (Giant Dragon's Claw Marks, Free Exploration)

452.text:
I'm Manual! It is a twin striker who will become a hero someday! 
 It seems that the Bandit team has settled in "Bolom Ruins". I guess I'm going to make it a root castle and get rid of the neighborhood. 
 If I know the heroes I know, I won't pretend to see it! 
 But it's too reckless to rush alone. Especially the leader -ranking guy seems to be quite skilled. 
 Can you help me? 
 I always manage the surroundings! Please hit the Bandit's main ball with your hands! 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E300_05_01_03001"/> 1 (Bolom Ruins, free search)

453.text:
Hello! It is RIRI of blast archer. 
 An acquaintance asked me to restore old bow. This is a famous bow known for its extremely accurate aim! 
 However, it requires an unusual material called "Sanse grass" and "scopo ore" that is not used now, and can only be found in "Forest of Will-O'-The-Wisps". 
 A little in a place that I can get ... 
 When the restoration is over, it is said that you can practice with this bow. 
 please! This opportunity is rare! 
 Please help me for my practice! 

 ◆ Collection target (where you can get) 
 5 Sance grass (forest of will-o'-the-wisps) / plant 
 5 scopes (FOREST OF WILL-O'-THE-WISPS) / minerals

454.text:
Hello, this is SARAH, a spellcaster. 
 In Giant Dragon's Claw Marks, I found some traces of rituals using Imagine. 
 The flow of the engram is starting to be disturbed, and if left unchecked, the monsters of "Giant Dragon's Claw Marks" may rampage and attack the surrounding towns and villages. 
 I will cancel the ritual for me. In the meantime, could you calm down "<Value Type =" EnemyName "ID =" E002_03_0_03001 "/>? 
 It should be okay with the way Slaft taught me ... 
 Please, thank you. 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E002_03_00_03001"/> 1 (Giant Dragon's Claw Marks, Free Exploration)

455.text:
You're me! Musketta. 
 I'm dealing with those who are a little annoying. 
 I want to defeat the two "value type =" enemyname "id =" e500_03_01_03001 "/>, but if you don't defeat them at the same time, you'll be restored. 
 Since the timing is matched here, would you like to defeat the guy in "FOREST OF WILL-O'-THE-WISPS"? 
 I'll make the other bumpy. I asked! 

 ◆ Subjugation target (place to appear) 
 <Value Type = "EnemyName" ID = "E500_03_01_03001"/> 1 (FOREST OF WILL-O'-THE-WISPS)

456.text:
Senior Blitz Lancer Current! Are you doing your best? 
 I'm collecting ingredients for medicine at the request. Everyone is running around, but there are so many types and they are so excited. 
 I want you to help you! Can you ask? 
 I want you to deliver "Yosaiishi" that can be collected in "BOLOM RUINS". 
 There's a strong monster there, and we have to be bundled. I can't afford that now. 
 Would you like to be asked to help people? Please! 

 ◆ Collection target (where you can get) 
 30 Yosaiishi (BOLOM RUINS / Freedom Search) / Mineral
